                    <div class="author-image-wrapper">
                        <img src="/images/bs-mai.jpg" alt="ThS. BS. Ninh Thi Phuong Mai" class="author-avatar" onerror="this.src='/images/doctor-placeholder.svg'" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="author-details">
                        <h3 class="author-name">ThS. BS. Ninh Thi Phuong Mai</h3>
                        <p class="author-title"><i class="fas fa-hospital"></i> General Pediatrics Department – E Hospital</p>
                        
                        <div class="author-bio">
                            <p>Dr. Ninh Thi Phuong Mai has many years of clinical experience diagnosing and treating pediatric patients. Her primary specialties include respiratory illnesses, allergy & immunology, gastroenterology, and childhood nutrition.</p>
                            <p>Dr. Mai translated, digitized the medical algorithms, and advised on the real-world clinical workflow design of <strong>BiliTool.Vn</strong> to provide a helpful tool for the medical community.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="author-credentials mt-4">
